# AUR (Arch User Repository) packages to install.
# One package per line. Comments start with #.
#
# These packages are installed using paru after regular packages.
# paru must be available (either pre-built in Deb/Arch/ or will be bootstrapped).
#
# Example:

formatusb
job-scheduler
mx-boot-repair
mx-conky
mx-iso-template-arch
mx-live-usb-maker
mx-packageinstaller
mx-snapshot
open-vm-tools
paru
uefi-manager
update-notifier-qt
